   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_NLS_42180_1828_08_22_page01.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <placeName ref="./Personography.xml#Edgeworthstown_IE">Edgeworth Town<lb/>
                  </placeName>
                  <date when="1828-08-22">
                     <choice>
                        <orig>Augs.</orig>
                        <reg>August</reg>
                     </choice> 22<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. 1828</date>
                  <lb/>
               </dateline>
               <salute>Sir,<lb/>
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#BeauF1">
                  <choice>
                     <orig>Capt<hi rend="superscript">n</hi>.</orig>
                     <reg>Captain</reg>
                  </choice> Beaufort</persName> agrees with me in <choice>
                  <orig>accept<lb/>
               ing</orig>
                  <reg>accepting</reg>
               </choice> for <persName ref="./Personography.xml#MarcJ1">our friend the author</persName> of <title ref="./Workography.xml#Berth1">Bertha</title>
               <lb/>
               your offer of three hundred pounds<lb/>
               for the copy right, payable at - six, nine<lb/>
               and twelve months from the first of<lb/>
               next December - about which time you<lb/>
               engage to publish it<lb/>
            </p>
            <p>Whatever may be the advantages of<lb/>
               the other offer which you made we<lb/>
               are contented with that which is here<lb/>
               specified ; and shall only further request<lb/>
               that the proof sheets may be sent to<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#BeauF1">
                  <choice>
                     <orig>Capt<hi rend="superscript">n</hi>.</orig>
                     <reg>Captain</reg>
                  </choice> Beaufort</persName> to correct who will<lb/>
                  let <persName ref="./Personography.xml#MurrJ3" cert="medium">Mr. Murray</persName> know when he arrives<lb/>
               in Town which will be in about a<lb/>
               month -<lb/>
            </p>
            <closer>
               I am Sir, - with due <choice>
                  <orig>approba<lb/>
                  -tion</orig>
                  <reg>approbation</reg>
               </choice> of your mode of doing business<lb/>
               Your <choice>
                  <orig>Obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>.</orig>
                  <reg>Obedient</reg>
               </choice> Servant<lb/>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName>
               <lb/>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
